{"title":"太行绝顶","authors":["沈仁康"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":12,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行绝顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈仁康"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行绝顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天有一个早到的黎明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带露的向日葵朝向东方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条山谷回荡着鸡鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旭日喷薄火红的光焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山岭岭涂上一片金；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染红了乳白的炊烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染红了云似的羊群。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵紧似一阵的钟声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾召唤民兵举枪迎击敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今这悠扬的钟声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼唤着，呼唤着出工的人群。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行绝顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山川如画，日出风景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳用它燃烧的颜色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描画山区人民光明的胸襟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的山，红色的岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行战斗过八路军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，遍地是胜利的阳光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太行顶上是更壮丽的早晨！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}